dataIdInfo.idAbs: This point data layer represents address points for Walworth County, Wisconsin in 2017. It is a feature class within the geodatabase, Walworth_Addresses_2017.gdb.[Point Feature Class that represents an address structure.]
dataIdInfo.idPurp: This layer is intended for reference and mapping purposes, and may be used for basic applications such as viewing, querying, and map output production, or to provide a basemap to support graphical overlays and analysis with other spatial data.[The data was created to maintain the County's E911 system.]

dataIdInfo.suppInfo:
Augmented original metadata with UW-Madison specific elements.
This data was submitted to the UW geospatial archive in 2017. Content may be considered current as of December 31, 2016. It was published to the UW geospatial archive as part of the Wisconsin Department of Administration Land Information Program annual collection of public data for the year 2017.
